Hello, I have an ad credit for $500.00, but it only shows up for one of my campaigns. I only have the other campaign set up to run starting tomorrow. Can the credit be used for both campaigns?

Hi there! Ad credits are typically applied to the account as a whole, so they should be available for any campaign you run under that account. However, if you're seeing it only for one campaign, it might be due to specific settings or conditions related to the campaigns. I recommend checking your campaign settings and ensuring both are set up correctly. If the issue persists, please reach out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
